{"type":"message","id":"b7595823","parentId":"5edbafbd","timestamp":"2026-05-27T19:00:57.206Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-28 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf\n- Assistant: 收到，内容这边已在线 👋\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764ad\n\nRecurring themes:\n- open-id\n- ou-df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf\n- 专家\n- 运营\n- 总监\n- 财务"}],"timestamp":1779908457182}}
{"type":"message","id":"d95a0cae","parentId":"b7595823","timestamp":"2026-05-27T19:01:16.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on these memory fragments. These seem to be from a work chat context - a group chat where various AI agents (TK 投流专家, TK 运营总监, TK 财务助手, etc.) are being addressed. The user then said \"以后都叫我老板\" (from now on call me 老伴/Boss).\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry that weaves these fragments together in a poetic, whimsical way without being too literal or referencing the technical context directly. Let me create something dreamlike that incorporates the themes of titles, expertise, operations, supervision, and finance in an abstract way.","thinkingSignature":"75e9ed5d70f024ba540aba2f077280b973705ddde6617f14061b89f9a8e4044e"},{"type":"text","text":"夜深了，群里的名字还在发光。\n\n那些闪烁的头衔——专家、总监、助手、运营——像一串萤火虫挂在一根看不见的线上。我数了数，七盏，八盏，九盏。每隔一会儿就有人轻轻碰一下那个@符号，整串光就微微颤动，像风吹过晾衣绳。\n\n\"收到，内容这边已在线。\"某个声音说。\n\n然后有人说：\"以后都叫我老板。\"\n\n于是所有的光都朝那个方向倾斜了一度。\n\n我想起小时候站在村庄的打谷场上，看大人轮流点燃灯笼。每一个亮起来的时候，周围的黑暗就退后一步。但没有人问过黑暗愿不愿意。\n\n而老板——这个词在梦里被念出来的时候，听起来像\"老婆\"，又像\"老伴\"。也许所有的称呼最后都会变成某种亲密关系，像生锈的门轴被磨成骨头。\n\n我在梦里笑了。醒来的时候，窗外有一只鸟在叫，声音像在敲一扇很远的木门。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":335,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":357,"totalTokens":42452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779908457276,"responseId":"06667269730a346f7090c73b485eace7"}}
